    <sec sec-type="discussion" id="sec1-1">
      <title>Discussion</title>
      <p>Self-injury[<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref4">4</xref>] can be prevented by timely interventions, it almost always occurs during florid psychosis. All patients will require long-term follow-up of their condition.</p>
    </sec>
